  &POTENTIAL
    PSEUDO_TYPE GTH
    &GTH_POTENTIAL
    2    0    0    0
    0.20022404942891       2   -9.12178553908842    1.70270770000000
       0
    &END 
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 12.0 
  &END POTENTIAL

&END ATOM
